data.description:
Located just 5 minutes South of downtown Parker, this stunning ranch-style residence offers the perfect blend of spaciousness, comfort, and modern living. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a finished walkout basement, this property encompasses approximately 3,209 square feet of finished living space, secluded in a quiet cul-de-sac. Discover the ultimate entertainment haven featuring a spacious media and game room complete with a sleek wet bar, and a small, discreet room perfect for a cozy retreat or wine cellar. This home offers convenient access to a wealth of amenities, including parks, the Cherry Creek trails, shopping centers, restaurants, and top-rated schools and access to the Creekside Recreation Center; which includes indoor and outdoor pool, playground, fitness center, tennis, basketball and racquetball courts. 

Brand new roof was installed on 4/2/2024.  Brand new exterior paint.
Beautiful artificial turf designed to conserve water.
Beverage Cooler Iinlcuded.
